  <!-- EN: Fire rat -->
  <RI_Animal_FireRat.label>火鼠</RI_Animal_FireRat.label>
  <!-- EN: A mouse weighs a hundred pounds, hair more than two feet long, as thin as silk, can be made of cloth. Constant living in the fire, always out and white, with water is dead, take its hair to weave for cloth.\n\nThese amazing rodents are rare, and their fur has the effect of protecting against cold and heat. -->
  <RI_Animal_FireRat.description>有鼠重百斤，毛长二尺余，细如丝，可以作布。恒居火中，时时出外而白，以水逐而沃之乃死，取其毛缉织以为布。\n\n这种神奇的啮齿动物较为少见，它们的皮毛具有抵御严寒和酷暑的效果。</RI_Animal_FireRat.description>
