  <!-- EN: Tian dog -->
  <RI_Animal_TianDog.label>天狗</RI_Animal_TianDog.label>
  <!-- EN: There is a beast, called the Tian dog, whose shape is like a fox with a white head, and whose voice is qute, which can ward off evil.\n\nThis is a medium size dog, its appearance is cute, IQ is not low, very loyal, and its combat effectiveness is slightly higher than ordinary dogs, so it is often raised by some women. -->
  <RI_Animal_TianDog.description>有兽焉，曰天狗，其状如狸而白首，其音如榴榴，可以御凶。\n\n这是一种体型不大的犬科动物，其外表较为可爱，智商不低，非常忠诚，并且其战斗力也略高于普通的犬类，所以经常被一些女性饲养。</RI_Animal_TianDog.description>
